6000|$|... "'Nonsense, friend <b>China</b> <b>Aster,</b> don't be so honest; {{your boy}} is barefoot. Besides, {{a rich man}} lose by a poor man? Or a friend be the worse by a friend? <b>China</b> <b>Aster,</b> I am afraid that, in leaning over into your vats here, this, morning, you have spilled out your wisdom. Hush! I won't hear any more. Where's your desk? Oh, here.' With that, Orchis dashed off a check on his bank, and off-handedly {{presenting}} it, said: 'There, friend <b>China</b> <b>Aster,</b> is your one thousand dollars; when you make it ten thousand, as you soon enough will (for experience, the only true knowledge, teaches me that, for every one, good luck is in store), then, <b>China</b> <b>Aster,</b> why, then you can return me the money or not, just as you please. But, in any event, give yourself no concern, for I shall never demand payment.' ...|$|E
